天...天黑了嘛 然後呢?
I mean,it's…it's dark. So?

24
00:03:17,250 --> 00:03:20,100
我們得走了 我只是說天黑了 我可以陪你們走...
We gotta go. I'm just saying,it's dark.I could walk you…

25
00:03:20,110 --> 00:03:23,930
我肯定比你更強壯 Ted
I'm pretty sure I'm tougher than you are,ted.

26
